    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271860/extras/4dfbc57dc26b29818f575709d2670cb6.poster.avif?t=1755522095\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271860/extras/4dfbc57dc26b29818f575709d2670cb6.webm?t=1755522095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271860/extras/4dfbc57dc26b29818f575709d2670cb6.mp4?t=1755522095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hand-drawn 2D metroidvania focused on fast movement, double and triple jumps, and the freedom to climb any vertical surface, including enemies to punch them in the face.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey to punch people I hate, those responsible for the hellscape we live in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect coins, increase your stats, and  combine elemental upgrades to become unstoppable as your freeze, burn, poison, and electrocute your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271860/extras/5be6f70ba697a2af6a0d035dc204dfd2.poster.avif?t=1755522095\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271860/extras/5be6f70ba697a2af6a0d035dc204dfd2.webm?t=1755522095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271860/extras/5be6f70ba697a2af6a0d035dc204dfd2.mp4?t=1755522095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Game Features</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic side-scrolling action, with modern trimmings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tight, responsible 2D controls. Dodge, jump, climb, slide, and punch your way through a multitude of different enemies and traps!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Double, triple, and quadruple jump as you increase your jump stamina!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover your own path! Explore the world for secrets that contain more bosses and extra upgrades!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evolve and become powerful with elemental upgrades to your punch, that you can both upgrade and combine together. Freeze, poison, and strike your enemies with lightning.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect coins that explode from their bodies to upgrade your stats. Punch harder, burn hotter, shield stronger.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A massive cast of enemies and bosses, brought to life with traditional 2D frame by frame animation.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271860/extras/1a5f8bc7e5a05ac70f8eba048f75f15c.poster.avif?t=1755522095\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271860/extras/1a5f8bc7e5a05ac70f8eba048f75f15c.webm?t=1755522095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271860/extras/1a5f8bc7e5a05ac70f8eba048f75f15c.mp4?t=1755522095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
